<p>
<H2>Software</H2>
<LI> <a href="word_sim_package.tar.gz">Word similarity tools.</a>
<LI> <a href="crawler_package-0.1.tar.gz">Basic crawler module: A host of Python components implementing a basic crawler for data collection.</a>
<LI> <a href="archiver.zip">Archiver module: Presupposes crawler.  Creates archive of compressed text files,  WithTwitter data, can be used to store various augmented information in an Excel file, including page rank, and disabbreviated web links with title info.</a>
<p>
<H2>Recent Papers and Talks</H2>
<UL>
<LI> <a href="submitted_spatial_aspect.pdf">The Lexical Semantics of Extent Verbs</a>
This version of the work descending from
the "Generalized Paths" Salt paper is under submission and will be stable
a while.
<li> <a href="frames_hand.pdf">Argument Structure as soft constraints</a> (talk
given at Xerox Parc March 9, 2008)
<li> <a href="http://repositories.cdlib.org/ucsdling/sdlp3/1">
Interpreting Words</a> (current draft entitled: <I>Circumstances
and Perspective: The Logic of Argument Structure</I>)
<LI> Paths and the Language of Change (<a href="paths_change.pdf">pdf</a>, <a href="new_scales_paper.pdf">Old version</a>,
<a href="scales_hand-2pg.pdf">ps handout</a>,
<a href="scales_hand-2pg.ps">ps handout</a>)
<LI> 
Generalized Paths
(<A HREF="salt_hand.pdf">Salt XV handout</A>,
<A HREF="salt_paper.pdf">Salt XV paper</A>,
)
<LI> 
Motion, Scalar Paths, and Lexical Aspect
(<A HREF="new_motion_to_state_handout.pdf">pdf version</A>)
<LI> 
Frames and Lexical Semantics
(<A HREF="frame_perspective.ps">ps version</A>)
<LI> 
Two Kinds of Determiner in DP
(<A HREF="http://www.rohan.sdsu.edu/~gawron/lsa_hand.ps">
    LSA handout [postscript]</A>,
 <A HREF="http://www.rohan.sdsu.edu/~gawron/lsa_talk.ps">
  LSA  talk [postscript]</A>)
<ul>
<li> Handout contains a superset of the LSA talk handout
<li> Talk contains read version of the LSA talk, some
clarification of material in the handout
</ul>
<LI> 
Abduction and Mismatch in Machine Translation 
(<A HREF="http://www.rohan.sdsu.edu/~gawron/mt_paper.pdf">pdf version</A>,
<A HREF="http://www.ai.sri.com/~gawron/mt_paper.ps"> ps version</A>)
<LI> Universal Concessive Conditionals (<A HREF="nuccpap.ps">
ps</A>, <A HREF="nuccpap.pdf">
pdf</A>)
</UL>

