<li> <a href="http://web.mac.com/therealjanesmiley/iWeb/Site/index.html">
Jane Smiley</a> (Not that fond of <I>Private Lives</I>, but
<I>Horse Heaven</i>, <I>A Thousand Acres</i>, <I>Moo</i>,
<I>Ten Days in the Hills</I>, <I>Duplicate Keys</I> and <I>Good Faith</I>
are not only all stunning, but stunning in their variety)
<li> <a href =" http://www.wikilivres.ca/wiki/The_Black_Girl_in_Search_of_God">The Adventures of the Black Girl in her Search for God. G. B. Shaw.</a>
</ul>


